The paper deals with designing an algorithm for computing the p-curvature of a differential system, which involves numerical analysis and computations. Therefore, cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Algebraic Manipulation), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of matrices and matrix multiplication, which suggests that cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) could also be relevant sub-categories.
